Regarding this note:

   [Editor's Note] Further investigation is needed for the SR specific
   extensions to the TE tunnel model.

I believe you are fully covered here.  Looking at the YANG model definition [TSM]

https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/draft-ietf-teas-te-service-mapping-yang-08

You can see this has been extended to cover segment routing

     /* Import SR Policy */

     import ietf-sr-policy {
       prefix sr-policy;
       reference
         "I-D.ietf-spring-sr-policy-yang: YANG Data Model for Segment
          Routing Policy";
     }

Looking into this model

https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/draft-ietf-spring-sr-policy-yang-01

This appears to be well defined to include segment list and binding SIDs.

